OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1773338768
OL,3,CRemains of Glasgow building destroyed
OL,4,Cby fire to be demolished
OL,6,FThe remains of a B-listed Victorian
OL,7,Fbuilding ravaged by a huge fire in
OL,8,FGlasgow will have to be demolished,
OL,9,Fthe council has confirmed.
OL,11,FOnly the facade of Union Corner, a
OL,12,Fhistorical building dating back to
OL,13,F1851, was left standing after the
OL,14,Fblaze on Sunday, which started in a
OL,15,Fvape shop on Union Street, before the
OL,16,Fspreading onto Gordon Street.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
