FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30302
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1773338768
OL,3,CRemains of Glasgow building destroyed
OL,4,Cby fire to be demolished
OL,6,FThe fire also caused major travel
OL,7,Fdisruption, with trains to and from
OL,8,Fnearby Glasgow Central Station
OL,9,Fsuspended. Scotland's busiest station
OL,10,Fstill remains largely closed and could
OL,11,Fre-open on a "phased basis".
OL,13,FGlasgow City Council said in a
OL,14,Fstatement on Thursday: "After a full
OL,15,Fand final assessment of the remaining
OL,16,Fstructure, our Building Standards team
OL,17,Fhave decided that demolition must
OL,18,Fhappen in the interests of public
OL,19,Fsafety."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1773338768
OL,3,CRemains of Glasgow building destroyed
OL,4,Cby fire to be demolished
OL,6,FIt added: "Scottish Fire and Rescue
OL,7,FService are still on site to take care
OL,8,Fof remaining hot spots".
OL,10,FNo timescale has yet been given for
OL,11,Fthe demolition.
OL,13,FMore than 200 firefighters were
OL,14,Finvolved in tackling the enormous fire
OL,15,Fafter the alarm was raised at 3.46pm
OL,16,Fon Sunday.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
