OL,3,CRemains of Glasgow building destroyed
OL,4,Cby fire to be demolished
OL,6,FAssistant Chief Officer David Farries,
OL,7,Ffrom Scottish Fire and Rescue Service,
OL,8,Fdescribed the fire as "very intense",
OL,9,Fsaying "the pictures speak for
OL,10,Fthemselves".
OL,12,FThe council update comes after
OL,13,FScotland's First Minister John Swinney
OL,14,Fpledged that details of financial
OL,15,Fsupport for businesses affected by the
OL,16,Ffire will be announced "very shortly".
OL,26,@xD@XOUxD@eO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/7
