OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1773338768
OL,3,CRemains of Glasgow building destroyed
OL,4,Cby fire to be demolished
OL,6,FIt has also been announced that a
OL,7,Fcross-Government ministerial board has
OL,8,Fbeen established to co-ordinate the
OL,9,FScottish Government's immediate and
OL,10,Flonger-term response to the fire.
OL,12,FThe group, which will oversee the
OL,13,Fdevelopment of a support package to
OL,14,Fhelp recovery from the blaze, will be
OL,15,Fchaired by Justice Secretary Angela
OL,16,FConstance.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/7
