OL,3,CRemains of Glasgow building destroyed
OL,4,Cby fire to be demolished
OL,6,FShe said: "The fire has left a scene
OL,7,Fof ruin in the heart of Glasgow and I
OL,8,Fam determined that the Scottish
OL,9,FGovernment will stand with the city as
OL,10,Fit recovers."
